@base = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{base}}/health

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ─── ANALYTICS ──────────────────────────────────────────
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Get Total Inventory Value
GET {{base}}/products/total_value

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ─── PRODUCTS ──────────────────────────────────────────
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2. Get All Products
GET {{base}}/products

### 3. Get All Products - With Pagination
GET {{base}}/products?offset=0&limit=10

### 4. Get Product by ID
GET {{base}}/products/1

### 5. Create Product - Tee
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Tees",
  "name": "Classic White Tee",
  "color": "WHITE",
  "price": 29.99,
  "collection": "SS26",
  "coming_soon": false
}

### 6. Create Product - Hoodie
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Sweaters",
  "name": "Oversized Hoodie",
  "color": "BLACK",
  "price": 89.99,
  "collection": "FW25",
  "coming_soon": false
}

### 7. Create Product - Coming Soon
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Pants",
  "name": "Cargo Pants",
  "color": "OLIVE",
  "price": 119.99,
  "collection": "SS26",
  "coming_soon": true
}

### 8. Update Product - Change Price
PATCH {{base}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 24.99
}

### 9. Update Product - Mark as Coming Soon
PATCH {{base}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coming_soon": true
}

### 10. Delete Product
DELETE {{base}}/products/1

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ─── VARIANTS ───────────────────────────────────────────
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 11. Get All Variants for a Product
GET {{base}}/products/1/variants

### 12. Create Variant - S-M
POST {{base}}/products/1/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": "S-M",
  "quantity": 50,
  "in_stock": true
}

### 13. Create Variant - L-XL
POST {{base}}/products/1/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": "L-XL",
  "quantity": 30,
  "in_stock": true
}

### 14. Create Variant - One Size
POST {{base}}/products/1/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": "OS",
  "quantity": 0,
  "in_stock": false
}

### 15. Update Variant - Restock
PATCH {{base}}/products/1/variants/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 100,
  "in_stock": true
}

### 16. Delete Variant
DELETE {{base}}/products/1/variants/1

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ─── VALIDATION TESTS (all should return 422) ──────────
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 17. Create Product - Missing required fields
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Incomplete Product"
}

### 18. Create Product - Invalid category
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "INVALID_CATEGORY",
  "name": "Bad Product",
  "color": "BLACK",
  "price": 29.99,
  "collection": "SS26",
  "coming_soon": false
}

### 19. Create Product - Negative price
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Tees",
  "name": "Bad Product",
  "color": "BLACK",
  "price": -10,
  "collection": "SS26",
  "coming_soon": false
}

### 20. Create Variant - Invalid size
POST {{base}}/products/1/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": "XXXL",
  "quantity": 10,
  "in_stock": true
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ─── ERROR HANDLING TESTS ─────────────────────────────
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 21. Get Non-existent Product (should return 404)
GET {{base}}/products/9999

### 22. Update Non-existent Product (should return 404)
PATCH {{base}}/products/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 9.99
}

### 23. Delete Non-existent Product (should return 404)
DELETE {{base}}/products/9999

### 24. Get Variants for Non-existent Product (should return 404)
GET {{base}}/products/9999/variants

### 25. Update Non-existent Variant (should return 404)
PATCH {{base}}/products/1/variants/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 10
}

### 26. Delete Non-existent Variant (should return 404)
DELETE {{base}}/products/1/variants/9999

### 27. Non-existent Route (should return 404)
GET {{base}}/does-not-exist
